{
  "texts": [
    "Regarding ease of use, ChatGPT ADA substantially reduces the complexity of developing and implementing ML methods by taking tabular data, suggesting how to deal with it, building the model, and outputting the results in the desired format.",
    "Not least due to its ability to communicate with the user, the tool offers a natural and effective way to work with ML models.",
    "At the same time, the automatization simplifies the associated workflow.",
    "However, as with any innovation, utilizing LLMs in clinical research and practice has multifaceted implications, from data privacy to data security to model interpretability, reliability, and associated ethical concerns [37] [38] [39] [40] [41].",
    "Upholding patient data privacy seems particularly challenging as-on the one hand-users may be enticed to disclose confidential (or proprietary) information, let alone sensitive personal data such as race and ethnicity, to use the model most efficiently."
  ]
}